  - **Slightly optimized** solution

---

Hope it is simple to understand.

---

**Brute force** solution

```
var brokenCalc = function (startValue, target) {
    let count = 0;

    // go down
    while (target > startValue) {
        if (target % 2 === 0) target /= 2;
        else target += 1;
        count++;
    }

    // go up
    while (startValue != target) {
        target += 1;
        count++;
    }

    return count;
};
```

